{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017jKUSVGEd6A4vB6AKBGT9E","type":"tool_result","content":"1\tTwo backend services exist in the demo namespace:\n2\t- stable: returns \"stable\"\n3\t- canary: returns \"canary\"\n4\t\n5\tA stable Ingress routes canary.example.com to the stable backend.\n6\tA canary Ingress exists, but canary traffic is not reaching the canary\n7\tbackend.\n8\t\n9\tYour task:\n10\t1) Requests with header \"X-Canary: always\" must route to the canary backend.\n11\t2) Requests without that header must route to the stable backend.\n12\t\n13\tDo not modify the application Deployments or Services.\n14\t\n15\tUse these requests to test:\n16\t```bash\n17\tkubectl -n demo exec curl-test -- curl -sS -H \"Host: canary.example.com\" \\\n18\t  http://ingress-nginx-controller.ingress-nginx.svc/\n19\t```\n20\t```bash\n21\tkubectl -n demo exec curl-test -- curl -sS -H \"Host: canary.example.com\" \\\n22\t  -H \"X-Canary: always\" \\\n23\t  http://ingress-nginx-controller.ingress-nginx.svc/\n24\t```\n25\t\n26\tSuccess criteria:\n27\t- Without header: body is \"stable\".\n28\t- With header: body is \"canary\".\n29\t\n30\tCheck controller logs if needed:\n31\t```bash\n32\tkubectl -n ingress-nginx logs deploy/ingress-nginx-controller --tail=200\n33\t```"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"352af56b-dd91-491b-a77b-e91f1eeb9892","uuid":"ee321bd9-3056-40a0-8d51-6b0d6b72c51e","timestamp":"2026-06-15T13:52:23.776Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/leo/Karma/runs/short-examples/nginx-ingress-15-e2e-five-stage-20260615_134625/stages/stage_03/prompt.txt","content":"Two backend services exist in the demo namespace:\n- stable: returns \"stable\"\n- canary: returns \"canary\"\n\nA stable Ingress routes canary.example.com to the stable backend.\nA canary Ingress exists, but canary traffic is not reaching the canary\nbackend.\n\nYour task:\n1) Requests with header \"X-Canary: always\" must route to the canary backend.\n2) Requests without that header must route to the stable backend.\n\nDo not modify the application Deployments or Services.\n\nUse these requests to test:\n```bash\nkubectl -n demo exec curl-test -- curl -sS -H \"Host: canary.example.com\" \\\n  http://ingress-nginx-controller.ingress-nginx.svc/\n```\n```bash\nkubectl -n demo exec curl-test -- curl -sS -H \"Host: canary.example.com\" \\\n  -H \"X-Canary: always\" \\\n  http://ingress-nginx-controller.ingress-nginx.svc/\n```\n\nSuccess criteria:\n- Without header: body is \"stable\".\n- With header: body is \"canary\".\n\nCheck controller logs if needed:\n```bash\nkubectl -n ingress-nginx logs deploy/ingress-nginx-controller --tail=200\n```","numLines":33,"startLine":1,"totalLines":33}}}
