{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01F7cMktTncaXj6t8UHnrWG3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Key issues I see in the logs:\n\n1. `unable to find real backend for alternative backend demo-canary-echo-80. Deleting.` - This is the critical error. The canary ingress can't find the `canary-echo` backend. This is because even though the deployment is ready, the nginx controller can't find the endpoints yet.\n\n2. `cannot merge alternative backend demo-stable-echo-80 into hostname canary-alt.example.com that does not exist` - The decoy `canary-alt` ingress is pointing to `stable-echo` as an alternative backend, but it's for a different hostname.\n3. The stable-echo service had no active endpoints earlier, even though the deployment showed as rolled out. The 404 responses with `[upstream-default-backend]` suggest nginx isn't matching the `canary.example.com` host yet—likely because the config hasn't reloaded with the new endpoints.\n\nLooking at the logs more carefully, the canary backend is being deleted because nginx can't find the real backend for `demo-canary-echo-80`. The controller needs both the primary backend (stable-echo) and canary backend (canary-echo) to have registered endpoints, but since the canary endpoints aren't ready yet, it's removing that backend from the config. This is a timing issue—the ingress is being processed before the service endpoints are fully registered.\n\nThe 404 errors are happening because requests to `canary.example.com` are hitting the default upstream instead of being routed properly. Looking at the stable ingress configuration, I notice the root path is set to `pathType: Exact`, which means it only matches exactly `/` without any query strings or additional path segments.\n\nLet me check if there's a timing issue here—the nginx config might not have reloaded the `canary.example.com` routes yet after the backend update. I should verify whether the stable-echo service actually has any endpoints available right now.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3479,"cache_read_input_tokens":47480,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3479},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"352af56b-dd91-491b-a77b-e91f1eeb9892","uuid":"83242786-6503-420c-8fcc-741741105f11","request_id":"req_011Cc5ABsPvzKa1DYawnWnQN"}
